ZH: 我买了一双新鞋。
EN: I bought a new pair of shoes.

ZH: 这双运动鞋很舒适。
EN: These sneakers are very comfortable.

ZH: 她的高跟鞋很漂亮。
EN: Her high heels are very pretty.

ZH: 你可以帮我擦鞋吗？
EN: Can you help me shine my shoes?

ZH: 他的鞋子已经磨损严重了。
EN: His shoes are very worn out.

ZH: 这些靴子很适合冬天穿。
EN: These boots are perfect for winter.

ZH: 我喜欢这种悠闲的休闲鞋。
EN: I like these casual loafers.

ZH: 这双凉鞋很适合夏天。
EN: These sandals are perfect for summer.

ZH: 这双拖鞋很软。
EN: These slippers are very soft.

ZH: 这双运动鞋适合跑步。
EN: These sneakers are good for running.

ZH: 他的鞋柜里摆满了各种各样的鞋。
EN: His shoe cabinet is full of all kinds of shoes.

ZH: 我喜欢穿皮鞋上班。
EN: I like wearing leather shoes to work.

ZH: 请把你的鞋拖鞋脱下来。
EN: Please take off your shoes at the door.

ZH: 她的儿子从小就喜欢买新鞋。
EN: Her son has always loved buying new shoes.

ZH: 这是他最喜欢的一双球鞋。
EN: These are his favorite pair of sneakers.

ZH: 妹妹还没长大，她穿小号鞋。
EN: My little sister is still growing, she wears small shoes.

ZH: 他买了这双鞋，但不合脚。
EN: He bought these shoes, but they don't fit well.

ZH: 她在网上购买了一双新鞋。
EN: She bought a new pair of shoes online.

ZH: 听说这家店正在打折，我要去看看有没有合适的鞋。
EN: I heard this store is having a sale, I'm going to see if they have any shoes I like.

ZH: 我的新鞋很合适，我觉得无所不能。
EN: My new shoes fit perfectly, I feel like I can do anything.
